{"tid":1477300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(求英文文宣)可唔可以用英文譯呢廿年黎支那強姦香港事跡洗外國傳媒版？","createTime":"2019-08-16T05:37:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T18:19:47.000Z","uid":114422,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"720e51055869e265d91604f8f7c44d34eec69ee9","tid":1477300,"uid":114422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:37:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B5Ka2fm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB5Ka2fm.png&h=4a9894e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本上就係譯番呢廿年黎強國怪叔叔點樣強姦香港小妹妹，然後係d外國傳媒fb ig洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n相信大家都會同意送中惡法並唔係事件既開始，但係我驚d外國人以為呢件事係單一事件，只要有一日正苦發神經撤回，就係BBQ大結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係如果佢地知事件係一連串，或姐會明白一日香港未有雙普選，就算冇今次送中，都會有另一舊屎我地食？<br />\n<br />\n但係小弟英文有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋d句子太省略得香港人先明，可唔可以用英文精簡咁寫一次，最好廿隻字以內，但係有重點？<br />\n<br />\n好似第一句係咪[2003, PRC hide the information of outbreak of SARS and let the infected patient traveled to HK and caused more than 200 deaths]<br />\n同埋[2016, HK government illegally disqualified some most-voted pro-democracy legislative council member]<br />\n<br />\n譯得好怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望d鬼佬睇完會覺得d Hong Kong people好crazy，點解會tolerate到chinese government 咁耐，一定要幫拖！"},{"pid":"003cbeed50ef2756526080f1955609aa625871b0","tid":1477300,"uid":89963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:44:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"941f1dbfe78025159ec8c2894b7f1140c57